                     <interp inst="t18311201-85-person771" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I received these books from Mr. Chadney; I gave them to the officer - they are Mr. John Noble's.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18311201-85-person772">
                  JAMES 
                  SMITH
               <interp inst="t18311201-85-person772" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
