                     <interp inst="t18311201-85-person772" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a Police-constable. I took the prisoner; I went with him to the prosecutor's shop - on the way to the watch-house he asked what I thought could be done; I said it depended on the evidence - he said nobody saw him take the books, but he supposed he should be committed.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18311201-85-person773">
